issue.title: http > slowloris attack can't start
issue.body:
preformed following steps to start http slowloris attack but the attack won't start
1- `http`
2- `[http] >> slowloris`
3- `[http] slowloris>> target example.com`
     `Target IP => example.com`
4- `start` 
   `[http] >>Command not recognized!`
